296
00:24:50,899 --> 00:24:54,079
Transponder and satellite coordinator, write the command script now.

297
00:24:54,079 --> 00:24:56,840
The staff in charge of the power supply, copy the previous energy level on the satellite

298
00:24:56,840 --> 00:24:59,559
