299
00:24:59,559 --> 00:25:04,039
In addition, the solar storm is only the most probable explanation so far.

300
00:25:04,039 --> 00:25:05,939
We need to wait for the result.

301
00:25:05,939 --> 00:25:10,319
Think if there are any other latent factors.

302
00:25:10,319 --> 00:25:16,100
Guan Zai. Since you're the chief engineer, stay in the loop. Report to me every hour.

303
00:25:16,100 --> 00:25:17,600
Noted.

