00:25:45,540 --> 00:25:47,120
   

305
00:25:47,120 --> 00:25:49,240
According to the simulation,

306
00:25:49,240 --> 00:25:55,600
we can confirm that before Satellite JX entered within our range last night,

307
00:25:55,600 --> 00:25:58,559
