311
00:26:10,159 --> 00:26:14,420
We have already devised a contingency plan for this.

312
00:26:15,039 --> 00:26:18,520
The reception part of the transponder uses analog electronics.

313
00:26:18,520 --> 00:26:21,159
It won't be affected by the single-event upset.

314
00:26:21,159 --> 00:26:23,760
Therefore, when the satellite rotates into our range again,

315
00:26:23,760 --> 00:26:28,319
transmit reboot command to the two transponders via fixed channels.

316
00:26:28,319 --> 00:26:31,199
If the satellite receives the command successfully,

317
00:26:31,199 --> 00:26:34,800
its telecommunication system should come back online.

318
00:26:46,324 --> 00:26:47,406
Attention to all divisions,

319
00:26:47,406 --> 00:26:51,453
